data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this charming 3bed 2bath home nestled in a desirable neighborhood. This delightful residence is ideally situated near Canyon Ridge High School and a variety of shopping options. The home welcomes you with a newly installed SS oven/range and boasts updates including newer carpeting and laminate flooring. Experience the ease of living with a gas furnace complemented by central AC for year-round comfort. The interior is adorned with a cozy wood fireplace, while the exterior offers a covered patio in the backyard perfect for relaxing or hosting vibrant BBQs. Children will delight in the playhouse & swings, set within the security of a fenced mature yard. The property is equipped with auto sprinklers & a 11x10 shed for additional storage. Enjoy the bounty of nature with a peach tree, grapevines, raspberry patch, garden space and a Chicken coop. This home is a remarkable find at an attractive price, offering both quality living and exceptional value.
